    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1873-02-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1873-02-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="83"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d83">
                <head>No. 389.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">General <persName corresp="#p_DES1" type="from"
                            >Sickles</persName> to Mr. <persName corresp="#p_HF1" type="to"
                            >Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Received Feb. 13—4.15 p.m.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-02-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">February</hi> 13, 1873</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your telegram of 12th received. Conference with <persName>Castelar</persName>
                    appointed for 4 this afternoon; time and manner of presentation to President of
                    republic will then be arranged.</p>
                <p>
                    <persName>Martos</persName>, who declined the presidency of the republic, was
                    last night elected president of the sovereign assembly.</p>
                <p>Tranquillity uninterrupted.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_DES1">SICKLES</persName>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
